ah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are seven martyrs besides one who is killed in the way of Allah: the victim of plague is a martyr, the one who drowns is a martyr, the one who dies of chest pain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14303,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/man-appears-as-martyr\/","url_meta":{"origin":14061,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Martyrs: A man may appear as a martyr, but is not","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: On the day of Khaybar, some of the companions were saying, \u201cSuch person is a martyr. Such person is a martyr.\u201d Then, they passed by a man and they said, \u201cSuch person is a martyr.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14057,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/08\/five-martyrs\/","url_meta":{"origin":14061,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Martyrdom: Five types of martyrs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe martyrs are five kinds: one who dies of plague, one who dies of stomach infection, one who drowns, one who dies under debris, and one who dies in the way of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4103,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/04\/sincerely-asks-for-martyrdom\/","url_meta":{"origin":14061,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Martyrs: If he asks Allah sincerely, a martyr regardless","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Hunayf reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever honestly asks Allah for martyrdom, Allah will grant him martyrdom even if he dies in his own bed.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1909 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064f\u0646\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/believers-die-plague-martyrs\/","url_meta":{"origin":14061,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pestilence: Believers who die by plague are martyrs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about plagues, and he said, \u201cIt is a punishment that Allah sends upon whomever He will